Package: savepointr
Title: Fault-tolerant savepoints for long running processes
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: person("Michael", "Bertolacci", email = "m.bertolacci@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Functions to create and manage 'savepoints', a method of saving
    intermediate states of long running processes in a fault tolerant manner.
Depends: R (>= 3.0.0)
